**A grotesque mask made of human like skin, twisted into terrifying expressions of pain and fear. Cinematic in its presentation, the mask is hyper-detailed and precise. Beautifully color graded, every inch of the mask is rendered with the help of the Unreal Engine, allowing for DOF, super-resolution, and megapixel level detail. The cinematic lightning brings out the intricate and insane details of the mask, while anti-aliasing, FKAA, TXAA, RTX, and SSAO ensure that every single bump, and pore is realistically represented. Post-processing and post-production techniques such as tone mapping, CGI, VFX, and SFX elevate the mask to a hyper maximalist level of horror. Insanely detailed and intricate, the mask is hyper-realistic, volumetric, and photorealistic, with ultra photoreal and ultra-detailed features that are rendered in full 8K resolution. Volumetric lightning and HDR add to the realism of the mask, and the use of the Unreal Engine allows for sharp focus and a level of detail that is unmatched. The final result is a horrifyingly beautiful sight, with the skin stretched taut over the contours of the guard's face, making them look almost inhuman. The expression on the face is frozen in a rictus of agony, their mouths twisted into grotesque smiles and their eyes wide with terror. The flaps of skin sewn together in an unnatural way, creating bumps where there should be none, adding to the mask's terrifying appearance. The skin is stretched so tight that it appears as if they are in a constant state of agony. In short, the mask is an insanely detailed and intricate work of art that is both beautiful and horrifying to behold. --v 4** - <@1016287988172456007> (fast)
